Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:03:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流通系统室下任室长 升迁顺遂组的樱井优太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识曾任职于
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松风物产流通系统科的盛冈森子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛冈森子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是小盛森
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小盛森?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小盛森怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了这份手册
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想这么优秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作能力应该也挺不错的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是发现她辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小盛森的确很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你从刚才说个不停的「小盛森」是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我取的绰号!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你们关系颇好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也算不上是朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上班打电话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替负责人接电话的就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话换人接听了 敝姓盛冈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于今天川岛不在 如果不介意的话就由我来受理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那待审文件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您发过来 由我来进行确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 小岩井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看情况似乎得请您稍候30分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才30分 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 盛冈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思啊 挑你忙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你的声音听起来好累哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明有特别注意这点的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂你的感觉 别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有累到非哭不可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边没有其他人的话你就尽管哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在也是一个人 小盛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你不喜欢被叫小盛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你的名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫 叫做森子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:04:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛和森
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小盛森吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有过这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 小盛森的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.71,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\fs120\be2\pos(1672.5,318)}松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.71,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\fs120\be2\pos(1654.5,421.5)}风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.71,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\fs120\be2\pos(1635,520.5)}物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.71,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\fs120\be2\pos(1617,622.5)}产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.71,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\fs120\be2\pos(1599,727.5)}系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.71,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-10\fs120\be2\pos(1581,838.5)}统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧 她现在在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆去找她好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 筷子掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大变得这么没教养 妈妈好伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小岩井妈妈 有一根掉地上了 帮我捡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是离你那边那么近吗 另一根呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉在椅子上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 干净的筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 都怪你没拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么就成我的错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹我是前辈 你也太没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉的是这双干净的筷子 还是这双脏筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小岩井 那两双既然都掉地上了 也只能是脏筷子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息时间快结束了 请你尽快拿双干净的筷子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放轻松嘛 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于您提议的庆祝康复外出用餐一事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事也怪我自己不够注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还让您破费
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在不好意思再麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉发生了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然收到了男士发来的外出用餐的赔罪邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给樱井先生发的回信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很努力去思考内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深怕有失礼数 还包含了我的真心诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 尽了我最大的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天心情看起来真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了它就万事搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想 好想赶快回去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太给力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下就可以毫无牵挂地上线了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是网游里的空气最给力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是凸击太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 小林 看样子你的问题解决了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听小紫说了 小林好像有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露馅了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怪她啦 大家都很担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在想你会不会因为个人的一些烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再上线了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 让你们操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是正好相反还是毫不相干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有烦恼的时候 游戏可是我的良药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 我很能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在从烦恼中解脱后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更能放下心来玩游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经解决了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 多亏大家 完美解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.97,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.5,186)}{\be3\fs75}新信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.97,SP3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,540)}{\fs67.5\bord4.5\be3\c&HC252F0&\3c&HD8C7EA&}莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.97,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(994.5,540)}{\be3\fs67.5}的礼物送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.97,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be\fs90\c&H2606C4&\pos(1200,550.5)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.97,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be3\pos(792,858)}{\fs67.5}确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.97,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be3\pos(1207.5,862.5)}{\fs67.5}关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉的礼物送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 莉莉送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果收下礼物我也得送些什么才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠了一份大人情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:02.75,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs82.5\pos(367.5,135)}魔法卷轴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:02.75,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs67.5\pos(238.5,628.5)}持有数3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:01.75,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\fs67.5\c&H1B2228&\k100)\pos(360,628.5)}{\r\fs67.5\c&H1B2228&}2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:02.75,SP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\pos(360,628.5)\k100}{\r\fs67.5\c&H1B2228&)}3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为一个男人确实会很过意不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照理说身为男人应该更加直接地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了将这百亿克拉的光辉献给妳而来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 林
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下我的真心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人都会想这样帅一回才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小林心里的男人魂到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得我的画风也大变样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢 就算要回礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然莉莉买这些装备都能毫不手软
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该挺有钱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想破脑壳要给她什么回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉她也都不缺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我刚玩这款游戏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们公会的Nico吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nico吗 我只有和她一起解过两三次任务
